description.en: Bankroll is a premiere decentralized finance network on TRON and Ethereum. It implements a voluntary, sustainable, and permissionless global economic engine. Through a network of financial contracts the platform provides rewards in TRX, ETH, BTT, VLT and BNKR. Bankroll... play to win!!!
